OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776888354
OL,3,CNowacki wins gold in the 200m
OL,4,Cbreaststroke
OL,6,FJersey breastroker Filip Nowacki took
OL,7,Fhome his first British Senior title
OL,8,Fyesterday evening (Saturday 18 April),
OL,9,Fafter winning gold in the 200m
OL,10,Fbreaststroke at the Aquatics GB
OL,11,FSwimming Championships.
OL,13,FThe 18-year-old won the race with a
OL,14,Ftime of 2:08:52, shy of his target
OL,15,Ftime of 2:07:00, but 0.99 seconds
OL,16,Fahead of the 2025 champion Greg Butler
OL,17,Fwho placed second, followed by
OL,18,FChristian Ryan in third.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
