FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776888354
OL,3,CNowacki wins gold in the 200m
OL,4,Cbreaststroke
OL,6,FSpeaking after his race, Nowacki told
OL,7,FAquatics GB: "I am over the moon,
OL,8,Fbuzzing, ecstatic and really pleased
OL,9,Fwith how the week has gone."
OL,11,FNowacki's gold win comes days after he
OL,12,Fqualified for the European
OL,13,FChampionships on Wednesday 15 April,
OL,14,Fafter recording the third-fastest 100m
OL,15,Ftime in the world this year.
OL,17,FThe Jersey swimmer will represent the
OL,18,Fisland at the Common Wealth Games in
OL,19,FGlasgow in July before the European
OL,20,FChampionships in Paris.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776888354
OL,3,CNowacki wins gold in the 200m
OL,4,Cbreaststroke
OL,6,FHe told Aquatics GB he needs to keep
OL,7,Fworking hard, Nowacki explains: "I
OL,8,Fjust need to see if I can step it up
OL,9,Fagain from the Common Wealth to the
OL,10,FEuropeans like I have done in the
OL,11,Fpast, and really give it my best shot."
OL,13,FSpeaking after his gold win Saturday
OL,14,Fevening, Nowacki told Aquatics GB he
OL,15,Flikes to challenge the Triple Olympian
OL,16,FAdam Peaty, he says: "I am enjoying
OL,17,Fpushing him, just as much as he is
OL,18,Fkind of pulling me along and pulling
OL,19,Fthe rest of us along."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
