OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776888354
OL,3,CNowacki wins gold in the 200m
OL,4,Cbreaststroke
OL,6,FAdam Peaty beat Nowacki by four-tenths
OL,7,Fof a second during the British
OL,8,FChampionships final on Tuesday 14
OL,9,FApril, but admitted that the teenager,
OL,10,Fwho is 13 years his junior, has a
OL,11,Fbright future.
OL,13,FPeaty told Aquatics GB: "I tell you
OL,14,Fwhat, we've got some talented
OL,15,Fyoungsters coming through the sport,
OL,16,Fespecially in this event, so I know
OL,17,Fwhen I do retire one day, this event's
OL,18,Fsafe."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
