FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776888354
OL,3,CNowacki wins gold in the 200m
OL,4,Cbreaststroke
OL,6,FCommenting on the race, Aquatics GB
OL,7,Fpresenter Dan Jervis says: "The things
OL,8,Fyou (Fillip) are going to do in the
OL,9,Ffuture is just going to be amazing.
OL,11,F"He should be so happy, he got all his
OL,12,Fprocesses right, he got the turns
OL,13,Fright, the length of stroke right."
OL,15,F"We were expecting something special
OL,16,Fand boy did he deliver, I cannot wait
OL,17,Fto see what he is going to do this
OL,18,Fsummer in Paris."
